♪Name the price of time♪

7
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,600
♪Make an appointment tomorrow♪

8
00:00:42,675 --> 00:00:45,575
♪Who will be nervous♪

9
00:00:47,575 --> 00:00:50,725
♪How to handle a crush♪

10
00:00:50,775 --> 00:00:52,300
♪Oh yeah♪

11
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:55,925
♪We’re on a level♪

12
