582
00:28:32,333 --> 00:28:33,333
Isn’t that normal?

583
00:28:36,666 --> 00:28:37,625
Hello? Hello? Hello?

584
00:28:37,625 --> 00:28:38,916
Pick up! Pick up!

585
00:28:38,916 --> 00:28:39,708
Hello? Hello? Hello?

586
00:28:39,875 --> 00:28:40,375
Sichen,

587
00:28:40,666 --> 00:28:41,958
