653
00:32:04,333 --> 00:32:05,325
We’ll go home now.

654
00:32:05,583 --> 00:32:06,583
Okay. Thank you.

655
00:32:06,583 --> 00:32:07,208
Thank you.

656
00:32:07,208 --> 00:32:08,041
Go home and take a rest.

657
00:32:08,041 --> 00:32:08,500
Okay.

658
00:32:08,541 --> 00:32:09,166
Thanks.

659
00:32:09,166 --> 00:32:09,875
