00:38:44,583 --> 00:38:47,000
Otherwise, I’ll feel
I mean nothing to you.

784
00:38:49,833 --> 00:38:50,541
You are right.

785
00:38:51,791 --> 00:38:53,750
I need to be strong.

786
00:38:54,291 --> 00:38:55,916
